Description:
SOLD BY NICK MAKROGLOU
First home buyers, owner occupiers and investors dont miss this amazing opportunity to secure a gorgeous Porter Davis residence that offers an affordable opportunity into the booming Derrimut market. Highlighted by a fantastic floorplan, the home comprises 3 spacious bedrooms, master with WIR and oversize shower ensuite, 2 living areas where the lounge can easily be converted into a 4th bedroom providing flexibility in design, and a lovely open plan kitchen /dining/ living area that flows beautifully to the outdoor entertainment area and great size rear yard. Other features include a superb main bathroom, large laundry with direct access to outside, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, stainless steel appliances, feature walls, low maintenance gardens, large storage shed, double remote garage with internal and rear access, double exposed aggregate driveway and so much more. Whether you are a first home buyer, planning to owner occupy or looking for your next stress free investment this cute and cosy abode should be high on your list.

Make Your Dream Come True

Description:
Open Cancelled Contact Agent
Joy On Jennifer!
Located in a prime pocket of Derrimut, this home is a dream come true for the growing family or any buyer who wants to move straight in with nothing to do. This perfectly presented single storey residence is set on a great sized block of land all within a short walk to Derrimut Village Shopping Centre, public transport, schools and parklands. With neat and tidy living spaces, brilliant natural lighting, and then additionally its large landscaped back yard you will fall in love. This four bedroom home boasts of master with walk in robe and large full ensuite with spa bath, large open plan living, dining and kitchen area with loads of bench top space and a great games/formal dining room at the front of the home taking in breath taking sunsets over Derrimut grasslands. Additional features include bamboo floors throughout living areas, hydronic heating, evaporative cooling, large gazebo area, two car garage with remote entry and internal and drive thru access, the list goes on. With such a long list of features, it's a must for everyone looking for a quality established home. Don't miss out, call now to arrange an inspection.

Description:
SOLD BY NICK MAKROGLOU
This beautifully presented and lovingly maintained home is an absolute credit to its current owner and promises to provide many years of joyous living and precious memories for the lucky new purchaser. The fantastic design comprises magnificent central kitchen encompassed by 4 living and entertaining zones including lounge, dining, family, theatre/rumpus room and alfresco. By opening the bifold door all these areas intertwine creating a huge indoor/ outdoor zone perfect for entertaining large numbers of family and friends. Providing privacy and peace and quiet the discreetly placed sleeping quarters include enormous master bedroom with WIR and twin vanity, oversize shower ensuite positioned to the front of the property whilst the remaining 3 good sized bedrooms are tucked away to the rear and are serviced by the quality main bathroom. Other features include stone benches, 900mm appliances, glass splashback, dishwasher and huge pantry to kitchen, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, high ceilings, alarm, quality window furnishings, double remote garage with internal access, double exposed aggregate driveway, great sized rear yard and gorgeous garden areas providing lovely views from most rooms of the home and so much more. With everything already done for you just move in, sit back, relax and indulge in the luxury refinements and upgrades of this special home.

Description:
Sudley Surprise
Proudly presenting this gorgeous Porter Davis contemporary family home with no stone left unturned, you can rest assure all the hard work has been completed. Boasting a flexible floorplan for every buyer with four oversized fitted bedrooms, master with large his and hers walk in robes and full ensuite, stunning formal lounge leading through to an open plan family meals arrangement and bonus rumpus room perfect for the kids to play. Executive appointments include a modern hostess kitchen with abundance of cupboard space, quality stone bench tops, stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry, gas ducted heating, evaporative cooling, massive outstanding pergola, double car accommodation with internal access and low maintenance gardens.
This prestige home presents stunning and is a only stone's throw away from all local amenities, positioned amongst house proud owners in the sought after Brimbank Gardens Estate.
- Four spacious bedrooms all with built in robes plus study (or fifth bedroom option)
- Master bedroom offers his and hers walk in robes, full ensuite (double vanities)
- Open plan kitchen which includes stainless steel appliances, 900mm gas cooktop, stone bench tops, glass splash back and walk in pantry
- The kitchen is located perfectly to incorporate the large meals and family area leading out to a beautifully built alfresco area with timber decking wrapping around to another large pergola.
- Separate formal lounge and a spacious rumpus/ theatre room
- Features include gas ducted heating, evaporative cooling and split system in master.
- Double car garage on remote with internal access
- All set on a professional landscaped allotment measuring 595m2 of land approx.
Avoid further disappointment as inspections are our pleasure!

Description:
SOLD BY NICK MAKROGLOU
Combining quality upgrades with dimensions of enormous proportions providing every conceivable accommodation space imaginable, this beautifully presented residence by renowned builder Metricon provides all the size and space you could ever wish for on the one level. The magnificent kitchen featuring thick stone benches, glass splashback, WIP and quality stainless steel appliances overlooks the family, dining and rumpus which then open up through bi fold doors to the fantastic enclosed entertaining room with bonus second kitchen making this home the ultimate purchase for those that love to host parties. Discreetly positioned, the sleeping quarters comprise master bedroom with an abundance of storage offering both a WIR and BIR and luxurious oversize shower ensuite, whilst the 3 additional bedrooms (2 with BIRs, 1 with WIR) being serviced by the lovely main bathroom. A leisure or kids retreat area that can also be used as a study or easily converted into a 5th bedroom and a large formal lounge room complete the home. Other features include ducted heating, evaporative cooling, alarm, video intercom, high ceilings, designer lighting, floorboards to all bedrooms, quality window furnishings including plantation shutters, double remote garage with internal access and double exposed aggregate driveway accommodating off street parking for 4 vehicles and so much more. Inspection highly recommended to appreciate exactly what it is on offer.
